abstract: Even if the company prevails in the costliest board fight ever, that fact that many big investors sided with Mr. Peltz highlights the power of activists.
snippet: Even if the company prevails in the costliest board fight ever, that fact that many big investors sided with Mr. Peltz highlights the power of activists.
lead_paragraph: But even if Procter & Gamble beats Nelson Peltz — something the activist investor insists won’t happen — how much of a victory would it really be?

abstract: Investors may be alarmed by Senator Bob Corker’s rebuke of President Trump, largely because of what it might mean for issues like a tax code overhaul.
snippet: Investors may be alarmed by Senator Bob Corker’s rebuke of President Trump, largely because of what it might mean for issues like a tax code overhaul.
lead_paragraph: When a senator says that President Trump is making threats that could set the United States “on the path to World War III” — as Senator Bob Corker told the NYT on Sunday — you might expect the entire business community to take notice.

abstract: Disagreements over whether to celebrate Christopher Columbus, who helped open the door to European colonialism, have raged for decades.

lead_paragraph: A reverend at Calvary Baptist Church in Manhattan appeared on the front page of The New York Times after he criticized Christopher Columbus, the Italian navigator who sailed to the Americas on behalf of Spain in 1492.

abstract: They were involved for years in triangles with Yves Saint Laurent and others. Now Mr. Cox finds himself the guardian of the fashion designer’s legacy.
snippet: They were involved for years in triangles with Yves Saint Laurent and others. Now Mr. Cox finds himself the guardian of the fashion designer’s legacy.
lead_paragraph: As two museums devoted to the designer Yves Saint Laurent open this month, in Paris and Marrakesh, there has been plenty of chatter in fashion and cafe society (what’s left of it) about the estate of Pierre Bergé, the pugnacious business brain behind the original Yves Saint Laurent fashion empire.

abstract: The vast majority of the newly created affordable housing units in New York City are existing apartments, not new construction.
snippet: The vast majority of the newly created affordable housing units in New York City are existing apartments, not new construction.
